// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XfjcRy hyperbola circle connector, 2024 by jt

// Connect a hyperbola and a circle C1-smootly
// (continuous position and derivative).
// Grey: circles and hyperbolas.
// Black: part circle, part hyperbola.

// TODO: variable circle offset

// other connectors:
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dsf3RB circular connector
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/McBczy hyperboloid paraboloid connector
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4cSyRK parabola circle connector

// tags: hyperbola, circle, connector

// The MIT License
